# Astar to Soneium Bridge Guide

Visit [Astar Portal - Astar & Shiden Network](https://portal.astar.network/)

Step 1: Select Wallet and Connect to Astar L1

![image.png](attachment:8f5a9783-bd94-4960-9539-486fa1dd946a:image.png)

![image.png](attachment:b03a4d16-59d1-4c33-83aa-ec74cccaf304:image.png)

Step 2: Choose Soneium Bridge 

You can also, visit from this link [Bridge assets | Astar Portal - Astar Network](https://portal.astar.network/astar/bridge/ccip)

![image.png](attachment:aa490ce9-7fef-4e13-8631-fc0efa38042a:image.png)

Step 3: Make sure you are on Astar Network in your wallet.

- Choose the Amount that you wish to send to Soneium Network

![image.png](attachment:5b7d4b0d-b50a-4e0c-b74e-db2e7db4bdd7:image.png)

Step 4: Enter the Amount of ‘ASTR’ and Click on ‘Approve’ and then ‘Bridge’ 

Note: 

- Check for Bridge fee and make sure you have some ASTR for Gas fees.

![image.png](attachment:1d7e6a37-a746-410a-b84e-ff1b77d972b1:image.png)

Step 5: Click on ‘Confirm’ Transaction on your Wallet ( Ex: Metamask )

![image.png](attachment:7dea7ce4-9ee7-4d7e-8f27-c2bf4bae751f:image.png)

You will receive ASTR on Soneium after 3 minutes approximately

- Updated Balance

![image.png](attachment:a4c55fd1-f706-45f2-8911-d697d1f18c23:image.png)
